name: ミタマ | Mitama | 神無き世界のカミサマ活動 | Kami naki sekai no kamisama katsudo
description:
Tagger:

Mitama, ahoge, thick eyebrows, short eyebrows, very long hair, blue hair AND green hair, bangs, green detailed eyes, flat chest, collarbone, red makeup

Note:

It seems to work well with the WintermoonA model, but you may need to test it with LBW for better results on other models.

In V2.8, the performance on chest tattoos has been improved (it works well with anythingV3), and the yellow pollution in V2.2 has been reduced. However, it seems to have weaker light and shadow effects.

As the chest tattoos and red dots still cannot be consistently stable on some models, I would still recommend using Photoshop for those adjustments. :(

Personally, I prefer V2.2.
